projectDesc.p: IGC-News1-eidfaxi is a subcorpus of IGC-News1 which is a part of the IGC-Project (Icelandic Gigaword corpus)that aims to collect as much as possible of Icelandic texts that can be published, under an open or restricted licence. IGC-News1 has an open licence while IGC-News2 has a restricted licence. The two news-corpora contain text from news media, online and written as well as some from tv and radio. Each text-collection is published in two versions, as two independant corpora. One is unannoted and each paragraph is contained in a separate tag (p og seg) while the second one is tokenized, lemmatized and morphosyntactically tagged..
